{"tid":2212180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大貓又領先一步!!","createTime":"2020-09-21T14:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T15:20:36.000Z","uid":374818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e2436c38c2ca31ce4e125afb1d8d415cb0469ca0","tid":2212180,"uid":374818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"大貓又領先一步!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFinCEN文件與匯豐銀行：外洩合規報表隱藏的騙局贓款<br />\n一批外洩的美國財政部FinCEN合規報表顯示，英國匯豐銀行（HSBC）明知有客戶涉嫌經營龐氏騙局，仍然為其提供服務，把數千萬美元贓款從英國和美國匯至香港。BBC Panorama 參與了這次跨國調查報導。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewstrad/videos/vb.592266607456680/2697257213880558/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbbcnewstrad%2Fvideos%2Fvb.592266607456680%2F2697257213880558%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=748b4b1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewstrad/videos/vb.592266607456680/2697257213880558/?type=2&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"7b1a82c30e4aee187d2748d348183e0ecd6fb73a","tid":2212180,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"我買佢跌到5蚊嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa481ca1e82e5a711f2647dadf44de7990b76d8","tid":2212180,"uid":374818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b1a82c30e4aee187d2748d348183e0ecd6fb73a","tid":2212180,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"我買佢跌到5蚊嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:00:57.000Z","msg":"5號仔配番5蚊  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed45d7a2ee49fbab837a39d2d8158827b77a87d","tid":2212180,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b1a82c30e4aee187d2748d348183e0ecd6fb73a","t